{"tid":387322,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台行政院長林全辭職","createTime":"2017-09-04T14:10:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-05T04:24:19.000Z","uid":3112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8f5cdafdf7bbc82d53b99edd7cc661f545d9b5b7","tid":387322,"uid":3112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T14:10:52.000Z","msg":"台灣行政院長林全在昨天總統蔡英文召開國安會議後，向蔡英文遞出辭呈，林全將在今午2時30分召開記者會說明詳情。<br />\n<br />\n行政院發言人徐國勇公開林全的辭呈內容。林全在辭呈上指出，他去年5月20日接掌行政院長，一年三個月來，已完成多項工作，他感謝總統賦予他為國家社會奉獻的機會，階段性任務已見規模，為利總統人力佈局需要，擬請辭行政院長。<br />\n<br />\n徐國勇說，因林全請辭，內閣也將總辭。至於總辭時間，以及是否由台南市長賴清德接任等等，徐國勇稱這都將待總統批准林全辭呈後，由總統府對外宣布。<br />\n<br />\n記者追問林全請辭是否因為外界盛傳將更換新閣揆而被「逼宮」，徐國勇稱，沒有什麼逼宮的問題，他自己也認為政務官上上落落是常態，並沒有留下什麼遺憾。"},{"pid":"8798f5fc246ff54cd2e223673c1d80b6ebe237e0","tid":387322,"uid":10626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T04:00:57.000Z","msg":"其實乜原因？"},{"pid":"bfd8ded3c4d5b45f72e96ae513bdea2e96d2b59a","tid":387322,"uid":58670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T04:03:02.000Z","msg":"賴清德接任<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1804ffb5f203bec8c1b282fcaa8d6b3f0740595","tid":387322,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T04:08:22.000Z","msg":"老男藍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d1d079ddae5e0cc807619db503635f9b1c90062","tid":387322,"uid":68094,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T04:12:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"36f818f1b0acdfca9d9138b87ec1ab4e775a7ef0","tid":387322,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T04:22:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>賴清德接任<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n親中份子<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec082ce6914ec7ce4ea8b45393443117f2737668","tid":387322,"uid":38651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T04:24:19.000Z","msg":"點解要辭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}